overview:
Shared is a free cloud storage service that helps people safely store, organize and share their media. Shared makes it easy to share media with anyone from anywhere whether you’re on your phone, tablet or PC. Your music, videos, photos, documents or anything else on your computer have a home at Shared.

Shared features a clean and simple design that everyone will appreciate. Along with a streamlined design, it also features secure functionality that takes privacy very seriously. It also boasts up to 2 terabytes of available storage space, making it hard to compete with.

Create your FREE account and start uploading today!

The best things in life are shared - share what matters.
